{
  "texts": [
    "92) by combining standardized gene counts and significant log 2 -transformed fold-change values from DESeq2 (Padj ≤ 0.05).",
    "Analysis of tRNASeq dataDemultiplexing and 3′ sequencing adaptor removal was performed using cutadapt v3.5.",
    "Indels were disallowed (--no-indels) and both read ends were quality trimmed with a quality score of 30 (-q 30,30).As sequencing was performed with more cycles than the length of any sequenced fragment, all reads were expected to contain adaptors and only trimmed reads were retained with --trimmed-only.",
    "The reads were further trimmed to remove the two 5′-RN nucleotides introduced by circularization from the RT primer with -u 2.",
    "In both processing steps, reads <10 nt were discarded using -m 10."
  ]
}